race.comment: SILENT CALL (5) has been in great form and looks hard to beat. Winner two back then narrow third here last time. Has the claim and expected to go close. SAN JOSE BOY (4) has been running on hard and hitting the frame the last couple. Close to a win and looks tough to stop. Same goes for CHAYSE 'N' PENNY (11) who has been in the money at his last couple of runs, the latest effort a third over 1975m at this track. Back in trip but drawn for a soft run and will wind up late. AUTUNNO (15) has been freshened since a disappointing run in town last time. Well back in trip and needs to bounce but best figures stack up. Don't underestimate. YUKANUMA (2) on the other hand will be out front. Low draw and could be over the odds.
